                    <ab>
                        <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/14">Carolus</persName> gratia dei
                            <rs key="#emperor/king">rex</rs> Francorum et Langobardorum ac patricius
                        Romanorum omnibus episcopis abbatibus ducibus comitibus gastaldiis vel
                        reliquis fidelibus nostris presentibus et futuris. Comperiat magnitudo seu
                        industria vestra, qualiter vir venerabilis <persName key="#Abbots"
                            ref="#people/15">Beatus</persName>
                        <rs key="#abbots">abbas</rs> de <orgName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/66"><rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/11"
                            >Sexto</placeName></orgName>, quod est positum super <rs key="#rivers"
                            >fluvium</rs> Edago in honore sancte dei genitricis Marie vel beatorum
                        sanctorum Petri et Johannis Baptiste, clementie regni nostri suggessit, eo
                        quod <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/13">Adelchis</persName>, qui
                        fuit <rs key="#emperor/king">rex</rs> Langobardorum, suo dono ei
                        concessisset ex fisco nostro, quod in <rs key="#palatium">palacio</rs>
                        nostro seu <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Marquis/duke #Public_exactions"
                            ref="#estates/310">in <rs key="#Curtes #Marquis/duke">curte ducali</rs>
                            nostra <placeName key="#Curtes" ref="#places/13">Tarvisana
                            </placeName></geogName>consuetudo [erat] persolvendi de <rs
                            key="#Vici #Rural_communities">vico</rs> qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Vici #Rent_in_kind #Public_exactions #Rural_communities"
                            ref="#places/39">Sacco</placeName>, qui est positus <geogName
                            key="#Fines" ref="#estates/125">in ipso <rs key="#fines">fine</rs>
                            Tarvisano</geogName>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Minores #Pigs #Rent_in_kind #Public_exactions">saligine
                            modia centum et porcos quinquaginta</rs>, nec non confirmasset ei
                        prefatus Adelchis aliqua <rs key="#Wood">runcora</rs> et <rs key="#forests"
                            >silvam</rs>, que est posita in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Forests #Wood">Rivaria</placeName> in <rs key="#city_territory"
                            >territorio civitatis</rs> nostre <placeName key="#City_territory"
                            ref="#places/12">Foroiuliane</placeName>, per loca designata, sicut per
                        ipsius Adelchis declaratur preceptum. Similiter innotuit nobis prefatus
                        abbas, quod fecisset <rs key="#Commutatio">commutationem</rs> cum <persName
                            key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"><name ref="Rotecari"
                            >Roticaris</name></persName>, qui fuit <rs
                            key="#gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldus</rs>, et dedisset ei <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">prata</rs> et <rs key="#Forests">silvam</rs> in loco
                        ubi nominatur <placeName key="#Forests #Hay/fodder">Crimastes</placeName>
                        seu recepisset in <rs key="#commutatio">commutationem</rs> de <rs
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >curte nostra</rs> in <geogName
                            key="#Commutatio #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/309"><placeName
                                key="#Commutatio #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Ripefracta</placeName></geogName>, similiter <rs
                            key="#Commutatio #Hay/fodder #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >prata</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Commutatio #Forests #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >silvam</rs> in <placeName
                            key="#Commutatio #Forests #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/19">Biberons</placeName> per loca designata, sicut per
                        prefati Adelchis declaratur <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            >confirmationem</rs>. Nos vero hanc causam diligenter discutientes una
                        cum fidelibus ac proceribus nostris ita invenimus, quod legibus ipsius
                        donatio ac confirmatio stare non poterat. Proinde anime nostre considerantes
                        mercedem et ipsius venerabilis viri attendentes petitionem denuo
                        suprascripta omnia in elemosina nostra iam fato monasterio per preceptum
                        auctoritatis nostre donamus atque concedimus perpetualiter ad possidendum,
                        ita ut memoratus Beatus abbas suique successores omnes supra memoratas res
                        quieto ordine ex nostra largitate teneant et possideant et ad ipsam casam
                        dei perpetualiter in augmentum proficiant; et nullus <rs key="#Marquis/duke"
                            >dux</rs> aut <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldius</rs> vel <rs
                            key="#Other_minor_officer #Iudiciaria">quicumque de iudiciaria potestate
                        </rs>est constitutus vel qualiscumque ulla opposita persona contra hoc
                        auctoritatis nostre preceptum audeat ire quandoque, sed omni tempore ad
                        ipsum sanctum locum perpetualiter domino adiuvante proficiat. Et ut hec
                        preceptio firmior sit, manu propria subter eam firmavimus et de anulo nostro
                        sigillari iussimus. Signum (M.) Caroli gloriosissimi regis. <persName><name
                                ref="Uuigboldus ">Wigbaldus</name></persName> advicem
                                <persName><name ref="Rado">Radoni</name>
                        </persName>recognovi et scripsi. Data iii idus iunias, anno tertio decimo et
                        septimo regni nostri.</ab>
